data.product_description: The ROCCAT Vulcan TKL Mechanical Gaming Keyboard is a professional-grade keyboard designed for gamers who demand the best performance. With its tenkeyless form factor, this compact keyboard provides a larger pad and a wider range of mouse movements, resulting in improved aiming accuracy. The keyboard features the innovative Titan Switch Mechanical, which was designed and built entirely by ROCCAT engineers. These switches offer a crisp, tactile bump and instant responsiveness, providing gamers with the feel of mechanical switches that they love. One of the standout features of the ROCCAT Vulcan TKL is its advanced anti-ghosting technology. This technology ensures that every key stroke of the most-used keys is registered, even during frantic gaming sessions. Additionally, the keyboard offers ROCCAT's Easy-Shift[plus] technology, which allows for customization by adding a secondary function to compatible keys. By holding down the designated modifier key, gamers can access double the command power instantly. The keyboard also features mixer-style media controls, including a tactile volume dial and mute button, allowing users to adjust volume and mute/unmute on the fly. The AIMO illumination system provides vivid lighting scenarios right out of the box, with full backlighting in 16.8 million colors. The keyboard is tournament-ready with a detachable USB-C cable for portability and on-board profile storage to ensure consistent performance at home and away. The ROCCAT Vulcan TKL is a durable and high-quality keyboard, with a reinforcing black anodized aluminum top plate and switches rated to 100 million keystrokes. It is compatible with gaming consoles and PCs, making it a versatile choice for gamers.
